{"tid":1668570,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣手足入一入黎]我今日行山見到啲咁既野","createTime":"2019-10-22T05:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T05:23:09.000Z","uid":145326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d39c2421f74fe8c975012d9c5811a4a985567c62","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:13:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我今日行城門水塘個陣沿途見到大量「文宣口號」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/66VjdCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F66VjdCG.jpg&h=dc40e844&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oTOT2v3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoTOT2v3.jpg&h=28a9e803&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPYEdCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPYEdCM.jpg&h=27ceb09f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/szuDua8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FszuDua8.jpg&h=9433379e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rjDT2wa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrjDT2wa.jpg&h=7594015d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSTEdCT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSTEdCT.jpg&h=62df4c4b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CF6eMXV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCF6eMXV.jpg&h=9e1e1425&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYAjdCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYAjdCY.jpg&h=8c413035&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n如果大家細心啲睇，當中大部分都係殘體字，仲要有啲口號根本係冇人會嗌(e.g華為收皮、鳩鐵亂插 etc.)。上面燈柱圖都已經自爆左啦，睇埋下面呢張圖就可以肯定唔撚係手足做，而且對面支那生番/廢老係想搞臭我地個朵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0jjX4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0jjX4G.jpg&h=4dee8f86&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6VBiubp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6VBiubp.jpg&h=96a1a4ca&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港歷史文物都畫?城門水塘紀念碑係港英時期留低既遺物，有錢都買唔番架。(我對唔住大家既係我影唔到班撚樣寫左啲咩，因為我上到去個陣已經有行山人士清潔緊塊紀念碑，所以大家可以見到塊紀念碑有啲一達達既黑色)<br />\n<br />\n文宣組可唔可以幫手出聲割席，呢啲明顯唔係我地手足寫/畫。無論用字、字體、字型都似大陸生番/廢老寫(上面西「環」亂港個「環」字都唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)所有文宣都唔會破壞香港古蹟/歷史文物，麻煩文宣巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3vZYdv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3vZYdv.gif&h=de033b65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a28de7b5a38b77a0346ed2eb43567cad86e99c23","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:14:30.000Z","msg":"支那仔唔識寫正體中文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e219b18d5d62b0b33b8924119a4fd7f4b369a","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"支那仔唔識寫正體中文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633807fd42bafbec8ee3e43c3367b0271458e6e7","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:15:31.000Z","msg":"支那仔唔識寫正體中文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6127b44d1e7f5c5fc4ba25b97ee402835231cb18","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"支那仔唔識寫正體中文呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb50825745080e694298e0a751fc4ad477d8cbaf","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d98fab99987424804702c77c726a8540766fc5","tid":1668570,"uid":224869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f2ccb4153c11f87e03a5ee753883ffb2596dbe","tid":1668570,"uid":143344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"推 之前已經有手足話搞政府嘢還搞政府嘢<br />\n港英文物就唔好搞到<br />\n唔知係咪有手足錯手啦 文物真係唔好搞到"},{"pid":"8fd7abe19e9aee178b1c094aabfe477386f132f5","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"環字都唔識寫，文革搞到你冇書讀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f044a4809f09b3210403ce51af3eb4f381333318","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"亂字都唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f50188cfc97dd276ec5d6535c429ee9734a7001","tid":1668570,"uid":145326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re